insert into `#__content` values ('127', 'Facts and Figures', '', '<p align=\"center\"><strong> FACTS AND FIGURES </strong></p> <p> On January 15, 1956, Christ Congregational Church officially organized with 41 members. A building committee was created on the same date, authorized to secure a church architect and complete plans for the first unit of a new church. On April 29, 1956, Kingsley Hawthorne was installed as pastor and the church was officially recognized at a special service conducted by the Denver Association of Congregational Churches. On June 24, 1956, a Special Church meeting was held to incorporate the church. One hundred members signed the official charter. On December 17, 1968, the name used by the church was changed to Christ Church (United Church of Christ), although the legal name remained Christ Congregational Church. </p> <p> The church&rsquo;s constitution and by-laws were adopted in January 1956. These by-laws were revised on December 9, 1958 at a special congregational meeting. Substitute constitution and by-laws were adopted in January 1967. Revised by-laws were adopted January 30, 1968. The by-laws were further revised in 1975 and again in 1999. </p> <p><strong> Membership </strong></p>  <p> The schedule below shows average numbers for five periods, the first four years of the church, 1966-1969, 1976-1979, 1992-1995, and 2003-2005. The number of new members taken in declines steadily, while the number of members removed remains quite constant, except for the final period of 2003-2005. Net membership peaked in 1970 at 610 . </p> <table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">   <tbody><tr>     <td valign=\"top\"><p><strong> Period </strong></p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p><strong> 1956-1959 </strong></p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p><strong> 1966-1969 </strong></p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p><strong> 1976-1979 </strong></p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p><strong> 1992-1995 </strong></p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p><strong> 2003-2005 </strong></p></td>   </tr>   <tr>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> New members (avg.) </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 108 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 63.5 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 32.8 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 10 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 11 </p></td>   </tr>   <tr>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> Members removed (avg.) </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 28.5 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 32.3 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 24 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 33 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 7 </p></td>   </tr>   <tr>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> Net membership end of period </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 363 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 565 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 372 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 288 </p></td>     <td valign=\"top\"><p> 250 </p></td>   </tr> </tbody></table> <p><strong> Budget </strong></p>  <p> Commitment to the church budget has increased each year of the church&rsquo;s history, significantly exceeding the rate of inflation. The table below compares actual operating income and expense for representative years. </p> <table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">   <tbody><tr>     <td width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"><p><strong> Year </strong></p></td>     <td width=\"55\" valign=\"top\"><p align=\"right\"><strong> 1956 </strong></p></td>     <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"><p align=\"right\"><strong> 1959 </strong></p></td>     <td width=\"60\" valign=\"top\"><p align=\"right\"><strong> 1969 </strong></p></td>     <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\"><p align=\"right\"><strong> 1979 </strong></p></td>     <td width=\"60\" valign=\"top\"><p align=\"right\"><strong> 1992 </strong></p></td>     <td width=\"60\" valign=\"top\"><p align=\"right\"><strong> 2004 </strong></p></td>   </tr>   <tr>     <td width=\"144\" valign=\"top\"><p> Income </p></td>     <td width=\"55\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td>     <td width=\"48\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</td